Long queues greeted shoppers at Eastgate Shopping Centre in Johannesburg as they rushed to make the best of Black Friday deals.The queue to Checkers Hyper was the longest in the mall and by 6.30am it already extended beyond the doors.Many of the shoppers said they wanted to use the opportunity to buy for Christmas while others were looking further ahead and stocking up on supplies for the 2017 school year. I have to buy stuff for Christmas. This is my best opportunity before things become expensive. I want to buy food and other items for the house. They (Checkers Hyper) have 40% discount said Thuli Mkhize. TMG Digital 